5gY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEKO65gY.jpg&h=b479e76e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡單嚟講 輪更制係膽，玩法就百搭。<br />\n輪更就係要班狗出嚟<br />\n佢一出嚟商場/街鋪就會落閘<br />\n借班狗嚟攬炒經濟<br />\n<br />\n而大家所付出既只係一日假期<br />\n<br />\n唔洗衝唔洗守唔洗打<br />\n如果冇狗<br />\n就做自己野，人多就會冇位企<br />\n黨鐵就會早收關站<br />\n<br />\n咁班狗出唔出嚟好？🤤<br />\n<br />\n有狗就街坊裝入商場/附近各自行街<br />\n一個唔小心，班狗就會咬到遊客<br />\n就真係外交風波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲狗走左就出翻嚟<br />\n做真真正正Be water！🤤<br />\n<br />\n輪更制！可能係全港最大既公司<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/letwechangeHk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FletwechangeHk&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=ddc208f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/letwechangeHk</a>"},{"pid":"51567ea2b90d4710e4128a98fcf47ae4ab3c2723","tid":1695554,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05c1fdf391ba7d7942e61d51743cdb284c96ba55","tid":1695554,"uid":54181,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:01:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:05:04.000Z","msg":"班魔警真係見人就拉"},{"pid":"573ccf3b45a2610d296e9719ffc9b578fab39518","tid":1695554,"uid":274793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0299c30e1aea54387e1dc3d2b143e5fc78237957","tid":1695554,"uid":261873,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:00:28.000Z","msg":"成班係大馬路等紅綠燈就被人拉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:05:31.000Z","msg":"唔係呀 真痴鳩線"},{"pid":"555c249d5b19eef03197da79f65ffaf0bd4c378e","tid":1695554,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:05:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce6655ec332c5922594368f413611584a2050a28","tid":1695554,"uid":254669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:06:24.000Z","msg":"有幾個女仔 希望冇事<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yTZJ7wE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"